description: Gem Wallet Token (GWT) is the official token of Gem Guard Wallet, a mobile-based cryptocurrency wallet that is used for trading, buying, and selling NFT's & cryptocurrencies. GWT is a chance for anyone on the platform of Gem Wallet to hold and own their very own (affordable) crypto asset backed by the platform itself. GWT has a burning mechanism that decreases its total supply and increases its value.
name: Gem Wallet Token
